Remember:

 - replace GSL dir with a brand new one
 - mkdir gsl-1.15/user_install
 - edit Makefile as follows

remove these lines:
IDIR_CUNIT = /home/zam/dev/hg/CUnit/CUnit-2.1-0/CUnit/Headers

IDIR_CUNIT = /Users/zam/dev/hg/laptop_local/repos/CUnit/CUnit-2.1-0/CUnit/Headers

CFLAGS_CUNIT          = -L/home/zam/bin/lib

and remove the ifdef/endif around these lines

ifdef NOT_ZAM
        IDIR_CUNIT = /opt/local/include/CUnit
        CFLAGS_CUNIT           = -L/opt/local/lib -lncurses
endif



Finally, replace this text

-L/home/zam/dev/hg/CORTEX_release/gsl-1.15 -L/home/zam/dev/hg/CORTEX_release/gsl-1.15/gsl -L/home/zam/dev/hg/CORTEX_release/gsl-1.15/user_install

with this

-L/full/path/to/your/install/of/CORTEX_release_v1.0.5.8/gsl-1.15 -L/full/path/to/your/install/of/CORTEX_release_v1.0.5.8/gsl-1.15/gsl -L/full/path/to/your/install/of/CORTEX_release_v1.0.5.8/gsl-1.15/user_install

(using whatever is the appropriate version)